  <brief_title>Efficacy of the Use of Risk Scores in Reducing Important Clinical Outcomes in Hospitalized Medical Ill Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>RICO</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy of the Use of Risk Scores in Reducing Important Clinical Outcomes in Hospitalized Medical Ill Patients: the RICO Cluster-randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
