    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Age ≥18 years

          2. Hospitalized for any cause in Internal Medicine

          3. Signature of informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Expected hospital stay &lt; 48 h

          2. Any indication for anticoagulant therapy

          3. Life expectancy &lt; 90 days
      </textblock>
